        <Meaning id="59aad89c-8fd2-4d81-916f-9033655f7195" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>được nêu rõ, được phát biểu chính xác</Vi>
          <En>Expressed clearly and explicitly, often in writing or speech; not implied or vague.</En>
          <Example>The contract stated that payment must be made within 30 days.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="7547634c-e546-427e-9902-27a8772cc9ee">
